      "rationale": "FDA benchmark experimental data were collected at 2.5 and 5.0 L/min at 2500 and 3500 RPM using bovine blood analogue. Simulation boundary conditions replicate these within ±2.1% for flow rate and ±0.5% for rotational speed."
