    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. The 6 non-assessed factors are consistent with MRL 2 scope and do not require formal assessment. CFD hemolysis predictions are within 25% of experimental measurements across all operating points. The relative hemolysis index RH < 1 criterion is satisfied for the worst-case operating condition. The model is accepted for use in identifying worst-case hemolysis conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
